{"_path":"/maps/_management/organization/organization","_dir":"organization","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"组织","description":"团队组织架构、管理方法、沟通方式等。","original_path":"content/6.maps/_management/organization.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"组织方法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"组织方法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_management/shape-up/shape-up"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shape Up"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"目标管理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目标管理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OKR"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"组织切面"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"组织切面"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_management/slice/standalone-data-engineering-team"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"独立数据工程团队"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"团队规模"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"团队规模"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"什么是两个披萨团队原则"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么是\"两个披萨\"团队原则？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亚马逊创始人贝佐斯提出的管理原则：团队规模应控制在"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"两个披萨能喂饱的人数"}]},{"type":"text","value":"范围内，即约 5-8 人。AI 出现以后，这一原则可能演变为\"单披萨团队\"——只需 2-3 人（含产品经理和设计师）即可完成过去需要更大团队的工作。这反映了 AI 对组织形态的深刻影响：小团队的生产力正在被重新定义。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#周刊摘录 见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2026/02/weekly-issue-385.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"科技周刊第385期"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"agent-teams-与组织架构"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent Teams 与组织架构"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"agentic-swarm-的组织架构陷阱"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agentic Swarm 的组织架构陷阱"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"企业将 AI Agent 简单替换组织底层的\"机器人版组织架构图\"模式存在根本性缺陷。这种做法本质上是将现有企业层级中的底层替换为一群 AI Agent,保留人类作为监督者——这看似熟悉且令人安心,但恰恰是最大的危险信号。真正的问题在于:当 Agent 能够自主协调和执行时,中层管理的\"信息路由\"价值被抽空,组织需要从根本上重新思考结构,而非简单替换。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的看法是,Agent Teams 本身就不是为了构建人类组织的数字化复刻,那是对生产技术理解不够深刻的人的自嗨,实际上 Agent Teams 主要是解决工程问题,和上下文管理相关。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.joanwestenberg.com/agentic-swarms-are-an-org-chart-delusion/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agentic Swarms Are an Org-Chart Delusion - Joan Westenberg"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"domain"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Domain"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_management/shadow-it/ai-accelerated-shadow-it"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI-accelerated Shadow IT"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_management/capacity-driven-development/capacity-driven-development"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"产能驱动开发"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"组织方法","depth":2,"text":"组织方法"},{"id":"目标管理","depth":2,"text":"目标管理"},{"id":"组织切面","depth":2,"text":"组织切面"},{"id":"团队规模","depth":2,"text":"团队规模"},{"id":"agent-teams-与组织架构","depth":2,"text":"Agent Teams 与组织架构"},{"id":"domain","depth":2,"text":"Domain"}]}},"_type":"markdown"